Overland Airways bụ ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọ elu nke dị na Ikeja, Lagos Steeti
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya bụ Murtala Muhammed International Airport, Ikeja, nke nwere ebe dị na Nnamdi Azikiwe International Airport, Abuja.
Ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọelu ahụ malitere ọrụ na afọ 2002 ma nwee ndị ọrụ 194

Gọmentị Naịjirịa setịpụrụ oge a kara aka n'ụbọchị iri atọ n'ọnwa Eprel afọ 2007 maka ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọ elu niile na-arụ ọrụ na mba ahụ ka ha bụrụ isi obodo ma ọ bụ ka ha kwụsị, na mgbalị iji hụ na ọrụ na nchekwa ka mma
Ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọelu ahụ mezuru ụkpụrụ nke Nigerian Civil Aviation Authority (NCAA) n'ihe gbasara re-capitalization ma debanye aha ya maka ọrụ.

N'abalị iri na abụọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 2018, ụgbọelu Overland Airways ATR 72-202 nwere nnukwu mmebi mgbe ọkụ gbara n'oge mmezi n'otu ụlọ na Murtala Muhammed International Airport. Ọkụ ahụ sitere na Ground Power Unit nke propeller blades nke ụgbọelu kụrụ mgbe a malitere injin n'ime ụlọ ahụ. Enweghị mmerụ ahụ a kọrọ.
